{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1772010801,"nonce":"6tLgw08q9HOzLIcAbdgFXaTS8O8=","title":"change_duration action implicitly granted via can :manage, Lending","message":"The `change_duration` action on Lending is not explicitly defined in Ability. It is implicitly granted to leaders and members via `can :manage, Lending` (scoped to their department). If `change_duration` should be restricted to specific roles (e.g., leader-only), the ability rule must be updated. Currently, both leaders and members can `change_duration` on lendings in their own department. Requires a policy decision before any change.","files":null}]}